Arduino Code for PAn Tit Control of the PAn-Tilt Stage
Originally written for Arduino MEGA 2560

Controls 12 motor
 The user enters the index of the number starting from 1.
 Or the user can also enter two numbers which would be the index of row and column both starting from 1

  Pin orderfor a given motor is
  Left, right, Up, Down

  Once entering the state: The user can control the motors using

  'a': Left
  's': Right
  'w': Up
  'z': Down

  Other letters stops all the motors
   To enter index: ENter like "3 4\n" for two index (row, col0)=(3,4) or just "2\n" to control the second motor where"\n" indicates the newlin character



